  <h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">

  <h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
    <a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/dezairedale">

    </a>
  </h2>

  

      <p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir" dir="ltr">putting the our into Labour, the purs into Spurs...and not only in Faversham for the Shepherd Neame beer...</p>

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">On Thursday let's be as ruthless to 289 Tory MPs who voted against Dubs Amendment to allow child refugees here, as they were to the children</p>
</div>

  if(window.ttft){
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('page', document.getElementById('swift-page-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('section', document.getElementById('swift-section-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('client_record_time', window.ttft.now());
  }
